        "richtext_P3nXP4": {
          "type": "richtext",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>BrightTools offers advanced technology soft bristle brooms designed to effectively remove dust, pet hair, and other low-weight dirt from all surfaces. These brooms are made from 100% natural rubber and silicone, ensuring they are durable and long-lasting.</p><p></p><p>The lightweight design makes it easy to use and versatile, and it can be used inside or outside your home. Our multi-purpose brooms are the #1 choice for cleaning carpets and removing pet hair in the broom category.</p>"
          }
        }
      },
